data.description: Located in the Heart of Golden Meadow, this precious 3 bedroom/2bath home is a MUST SEE!! With access to Hwy 3235 and LA 1- Ideal location. This home offers new metal roof, new HVAC, new floors throughout most of the home; bedrooms still have original hard wood oak floors. There is a quaint sitting area which can also be used as an office and also another bonus room with laundry hook-up spacious enough to be used as an entertainment room, man cave, etc. The Master bedroom suite has a very nice dressing area and a newly renovated bathroom with walk-in shower. Transferrable flood insurance. All measurements to be determined by the buyer or appraiser.
